extendedInfo.description: The Official App of Rosie Fortescue and atfashionforte, bringing you all the latest fashion styles from the self styled star of Made in Chelsea.Breaking down each episode of the hit E4 show Made in Chelsea, detailing each and every outfit she wears.Adding sections for her own style blog, Twitter, Facebook, gallery and video channels, this is a must have App for all followers of fashion.Rosie entered the limelight through the hit show Made In Chelsea, a show that follows the every day life of the young, wealthy and social residents of Chelsea. Being one of the original cast members Rosie is currently filming the fourth season of the show. Throughout the show Rosie has showcased her desirable fashion sense with stylish, modern outfits and has channeled her love for Fashion through her blog At Fashion Forte. Her blog that documents her wardrobe and fashion 'must haves' has become immensely popular, putting her on the fashion map.

reviews.title: Great App!
reviews.comment: Enables the user to view everything that would be on Rosie\'s blog in an incredibly easy to read format. Great to use when out. No faults! Well done Rosie!
reviews.author: Emelia Garvie

reviews.title: Great!
reviews.comment: Cool app, lots to look at, very impressive great job Ms. Fortescue. I love that you have the episodes on there too
reviews.author: Abby Kirwan

reviews.title: Nice slick look
reviews.comment: Nice easy to use and can catch up with rosies fashion onbthe go
